Dave Kroupa watched his cell phone blow up with dozens of text messages from his stalker.

ANALYSIS: Often we are told we must stay in the present in order to appreciate what is right in front of us and stay in a place of peace.

Though what do we do about our past, and what do we plan or envision for our future? Via @matthewjdowd. https://t.co/LDF1KHHJAa
